Comment: 0,0:00:01.02,0:02:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sound that could even wake the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:51.21,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,85.333333)}A Day in the Troop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:51.21,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,434)}Rio Runs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm digging in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a local dish from my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they call "miso"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made using the same method as soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some of Mom's miso here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So have as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A message from the supply corps finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan and I will go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're low on ammunition, medicine, and everyday supplies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to Carl-san's workshop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:03:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to train you fiercely this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your father saw this, he'd probably cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't like them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids at the church didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using useless superstition to make money. It's the same all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not quite true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones here are quite delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.65,PaperPlane,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz7\pos(311.375,89.333333)}Great Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems like Kana-chan is getting used to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is cute, working hard everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do agree that she's enthusiastic and diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if one thinks that those qualities alone will suffice, they're too naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Se~cr~et.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.66,PaperPlane,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz20\pos(441.225,52)}Great Misfortune{Mo French}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably be late when we return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give Rio-senpai any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceeding with departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't expect you to do it at this level,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using the mouthpiece to control sound is a fundamental skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you finding life here?{If QC can give me a better phrasing, I'll take it}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like you to say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little jealous of that sanguine personality of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right. Why did you want to join the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you could learn an instrument for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... um... p-protecting the country is also important!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that. I won't judge whether it's for money or other reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have a clear goal persevere longer than those who don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Rio-senpai, why did you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right. I guess it's because of the exact opposite reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, these sure are rare nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially brass instruments. You don't hear them outside the army anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, I heard one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound... of... the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Get ahold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ahold of yourself, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop moving so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot... Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat... snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow... Snow... Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would we even have that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... That's only as a last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine... Medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine... Medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're low on various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those idiots in the supply corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the children do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely apologize for my past behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me.{say no pls}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although her temperature is still quite high,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not some severe sickness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's probably tertian malaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tertian malaria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't only children get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults can get it as well if they happen to be severely exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:13:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new kids that are brought to us often get it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem fine at first, but then suddenly they have a high fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have endured it for a while. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, will Kanata recover?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't stay this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she will be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Although these are just medicinal herbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a little while, and then have her drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to serve this city is our joy and also our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, may you be blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just like miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff from the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miso dregs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you make miso soup, you strain out the miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beans and such that are left over are the dregs.{Dregs might sound better...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff that is extra or useless. Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been like that since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to try hard this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:17:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to drag everyone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a lot more fragile than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're also stubborn and like to be spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I... say... something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song that you were humming earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive. You've only heard it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could play that piece as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...want to sing a song that seems to resound from the sky. {Can fancy this up if you'd like. Resound from the sky, etc. She's quite dreamy, but this is more literal trans}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that miso is... miso no matter what, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be indebted to the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi is a product from a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And within this guy sleeps various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Various?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Noël for specifics later.{THE FUCK THEY HAVE THIS KIND OF TECHNOLOGY?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably what the complete song sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are various instruments playing, and their sounds harmonize together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They become a single unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like tank crews.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, gunner, driver, and communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone works together; that's how a tank is able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no notes that are not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that.{creep} It was something I was told.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one I admired and respected the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I use her words...{it's technically ambiguous, but from the flashbacks, it's probably that blonde girl...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think senpai and superiors exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so that their juniors can trouble them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you aren't able to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember how it felt being frustrated and powerless,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the happiness of someone caring for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, some day, when you need to protect others...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll definitely be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, cause as much trouble as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you'll get scolded and punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if it's difficult, then say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'll give you lots and lots of trouble!{you asked for it}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go easy on me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I knew I should have stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually getting cared for by Rio-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It was nothing. She was just too tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine after some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemikazuchi's lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Sorry, I used it for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listened to that song, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you wouldn't listen to it anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
